4:71 EOL "\n"
5:1 COMMENT "# are accessible from outside the type definition."
5:51 EOL "\n"
6:1 EOL "\n"
7:1 COMMENT "# Record with restricted public interface: the private `_dist` field"
7:69 EOL "\n"
8:1 COMMENT "# stays reachable through the public `dist` method."
